# ESP32-C6 specific configuration - ESP-IDF 6.0
# ESP32-C6 is a RISC-V MCU with native IEEE 802.11b/g/n/ax WiFi (WiFi 6)
# Standard C6 dev boards have no external PSRAM; disable SPIRAM from base config.
# No esp_hosted/wifi_remote needed: native WiFi stack is used directly.
# CONFIG_SPIRAM is not set
